		<a name="top" id="top"></a>
				<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Enabling the Root Account</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From OpenStora</h3>
			<div id="contentSub">
				<div id="mw-revision-info">Revision as of 22:03, 4 November 2010 by <a href="/wiki/index.php?title=User:Smiff&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new mw-userlink" title="User:Smiff (page does not exist)">Smiff</a>  <span class="mw-usertoollinks">(<a href="/wiki/index.php?title=User_talk:Smiff&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="User talk:Smiff (page does not exist)">Talk</a>&#32;|&#32;<a href="/wiki/index.php?title=Special:Contributions/Smiff" title="Special:Contributions/Smiff">contribs</a>)</span></div>

				<div id="mw-revision-nav">(<a href="/wiki/index.php?title=Enabling_the_Root_Account&amp;diff=prev&amp;oldid=503" title="Enabling the Root Account">diff</a>) <a href="/wiki/index.php?title=Enabling_the_Root_Account&amp;direction=prev&amp;oldid=503" title="Enabling the Root Account">← Older revision</a>&#32;|&#32;Latest revision (diff)&#32;|&#32;Newer revision → (diff)</div>
